<p class="note-body">This section is referred to in <uscode edition="1995" range="215c, 461, 1464, 1467a, 1814, 1816, 1821, 3104" section="215c" title="12">sections 215c, 461, 1464, 1467a, 1814, 1816, 1821, 3104 of this title</uscode>.</p>
