<h4 class="note-head">Cross References</h4>
<p class="note-body">Penalties for making or inviting reliance on false, forged, or counterfeit statement, document, or thing, to influence action of Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation, see <uscode edition="1995" section="1007" title="18">section 1007 of Title 18</uscode>, Crimes and Criminal Procedure.</p>
<!-- field-end:crossreference-note -->
