<h4 class="note-head">Change of Name</h4>
<p class="note-body">Oversight Board redesignated Thrift Depositor Protection Oversight Board, effective Feb. 1, 1992, see section 302(a) of <plaw congress="102" isprivate="false" number="233">Pub. L. 102–233,</plaw> set out as a note under <uscode edition="1995" section="1441a" title="12">section 1441a of this title</uscode>.</p>
<!-- field-end:changeofname-note -->
