<p class="note-body">Section 202 of <plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="104">Pub. L. 96–104,</plaw> cited as a credit to this section, was repealed by section 212 of <plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="161">Pub. L. 96–161,</plaw> effective at the close of Dec. 27, 1979. The amendment of this section by that repealed provision, described in the 1979 Amendment note set out under this section, shall continue in effect for limited purposes pursuant to section 212 of <plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="161">Pub. L. 96–161</plaw>. See Savings Provisions note, describing the provisions of section 212 of <plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="161">Pub. L. 96–161,</plaw> set out under <uscode edition="1995" section="85" title="12">section 85 of this title</uscode>.</p>
